      "file_path": "catalog-ui/src/app/ng2/components/logic/service-dependencies/service-dependencies.component.ts",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 171,
      "message": "in TOSCA syntax it is define as list. we should support it and not have this restriction.\nfrom TOSCA spec: \ndirectives\t| no\t| list of string\t| An optional list of directive values to provide processing instructions to orchestrators and tooling.",
